# GitHub Issues Rules
- Only create issues on the repo `chand1012/clive-py`.
- Be clear and detailed as possible whenever creating issues.
- When creating bug reports, include as much context about the bug as possible, including but not limited to:
  - Git commit hash and branch
  - Python version
  - Command executed
  - Error logs
  - Hardware information
  - Operating system information
  - Any other relevant information about files or the system.
- When creating feature requests, include as much detail as possible about what the feature should do and how it should do it.
